\frac{1}{1+\frac{1}{z}}=\frac{1}{1-\frac{-1}{z}}=\sum_{k=0}^\infty \left( \frac{-1}{z}\right)^k=\sum_{k=0}^\infty \frac{(-1)^k}{z^k}
